{"tid":1031401,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖]求救 幾千蚊一隻大陸手環係咪騙局","createTime":"2019-02-21T15:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T04:37:37.000Z","uid":176999,"like":16,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"51b556fef4ab2a1bdd98dc9948ade0e8425a06e3","tid":1031401,"uid":176999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T15:26:49.000Z","msg":"話説我親戚送左隻手環俾家母, 話可以用三至五年都唔叉電, 又冇叉電接口 <br />\n<br />\n仲話隻野可以check到身體健康情況 包括腸胃問題, 器官問題, 腎問題, 家母用佢個專用app黎check完話自己腸胃係最唔好,話講中左, 信到十足十咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我發覺唔多妥,追問落去 ,佢就話個親戚用左幾千蚊買俾佢, 隻手環個名叫'脉xx', 仲話可以發放負離子令身體更健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又話一隻手環只可以一個人一架手機用 其他人用用唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但之後又話俾多d錢登記,將資料入落部電話,每年俾年費就可以一齊用到一條手環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上網搵一搵,dllm,吹到連病理, 微生物,過敏原,污染物都話掃瞄到,仲話咩大數據,雲端,區塊鏈技術 , 講埋話要改變世界 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係香港搞埋展銷會推銷, 家母仲話佢同事都有送俾屋企人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位巴打,到底係小弟知識貧乏唔識高科技野定係騙局？呢間係咩公司咩手環黎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h7Ktm3t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh7Ktm3t.jpg&h=84851082&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nB1SOJu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnB1SOJu.jpg&h=6144c19f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/toR3Vou.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtoR3Vou.jpg&h=3d5649ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cfaad20ad686fdb46aadb562322c937094c5abb8","tid":1031401,"uid":136186,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T15:28:26.000Z","msg":"真嘢嚟 攞住佢對住癌症病人半個鐘會醫返好"},{"pid":"8df5c130139cd44aef71ef60bf1e568f98f98069","tid":1031401,"uid":60412,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"